      • addDirectionFile

        public abstract WeatherGrid.WeatherGridGridFile addDirectionFile(String filename,
                                                                 String projection,
                                                                 WeatherGridSector sector,
                                                                 double speed)
                                                          throws Exception
        Add a direction file to the weather grid.
        Parameters:
        filename - The location of the grid file.
        projection - The projection file.
        sector - The sector (wind direction) to apply this grid file to. Only one of each sector is allowed per station.
        speed - The wind speed.
        Returns:
        The new direction file.
        Throws:
        Exception
